ly our VN-Transformer to 3D shape classification and motion forecasting with\ncompelling results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 8 Jun 2022 21:48:47 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 21 Oct 2022 14:23:31 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 24 Jan 2023 20:27:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-01-26"}
