ls of actinides compared to those of lanthanides.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 02:47:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 24 Aug 2022 08:12:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-25"}
