lexity) solutions.\nExperimental results demonstrate the effectiveness of our proposed hybrid\nworker recruitment mechanism in terms of service quality, time efficiency, etc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 08:55:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 27 Jul 2022 04:34:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-28"}
