 other proposed magnetic architectures in the signal\ntransformation and spoken digit recognition tasks, and provides, to the\nauthor's knowledge, the first experimental demonstration of NARMA time series\nprediction in a nanomagnetic platform without the use of external delay lines.\nThis constitutes a critical step forward in the design of In Materio\ncomputation devices which can exploit the rich dynamics offered by emergent\nsystems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 9 Jun 2022 12:14:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 5 Aug 2022 13:50:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-08"}
